original_title: They Might Be Giants: The Videos 1986-1989
overview: John Flansburgh and John Linnell are They Might Be Giants. The duo released it's debut record in 1986 on the small Hoboken, New Jersey based bar/None records. From their first, to the most recent , these videos display the kind of visual and musical inventiveness that have catapulted the twin quasars to their rightful place in the rock Galaxy.
title: They Might Be Giants: The Videos 1986-1989
